Package: scReportLite
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Interactive HTML Report Generator
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Kee-gong Karios",
                  family = "Park",
                  email = "karioslion0517@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate portable interactive HTML report bundles from single-cell
    RNA-seq analysis results. Accepts UMAP coordinates, cluster assignments, and
    marker gene tables, producing an HTML entry file plus its dependency folder
    with interactive cluster highlighting and marker table display.
